<span>.</span><span>.</span></span></span></div></pre></div>\n<h2> </h2>\n<h3>应用</h3>\n<h4>测试</h4>\n<div class='midnight'><pre class=\"editor editor-colors\"><div class=\"line\"><span class=\"syntax--source syntax--ruby\"><span>$&nbsp;hexo&nbsp;server</span></span></div></pre></div>\n<p>可以访问 <a href=\"http://localhost:4000\">http://localhost:4000</a> 查看效果</p>\n<h4>生成静态文件</h4>\n<div class='midnight'><pre class=\"editor editor-colors\"><div class=\"line\"><span class=\"syntax--source syntax--ruby\"><span>$&nbsp;hexo&nbsp;generate</span></span></div></pre></div>\n<h2> </h2>\n<h3>部署</h3>\n<p>修改 _config.yml 文件</p>\n<div class='midnight'><pre class=\"editor editor-colors\"><div class=\"line\"><span class=\"syntax--source syntax--ruby\"><span class=\"syntax--punctuation syntax--separator syntax--method syntax--ruby\"><span>.</span><span>.</span><span>.</span></span></span></div><div class=\"line\"><span class=\"syntax--source syntax--ruby\"><span class=\"syntax--constant syntax--other syntax--symbol syntax--hashkey syntax--ruby\"><span>deploy</span><span class=\"syntax--punctuation syntax--definition syntax--constant syntax--ruby\"><span>:</span></span></span></span></div><div class=\"line\"><span class=\"syntax--source syntax--ruby\"><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span class=\"syntax--constant syntax--other syntax--symbol syntax--hashkey syntax--ruby\"><span>type</span><span class=\"syntax--punctuation syntax--definition syntax--constant syntax--ruby\"><span>:</span></span></span><span>&nbsp;git</span></span></div><div class=\"line\"><span class=\"syntax--source syntax--ruby\"><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span class=\"syntax--constant syntax--other syntax--symbol syntax--hashkey syntax--ruby\"><span>repository</span><span class=\"syntax--punctuation syntax--definition syntax--constant syntax--ruby\"><span>:</span></span></span><span>&nbsp;</span><span class=\"syntax--constant syntax--other syntax--symbol syntax--hashkey syntax--ruby\"><span>https</span><span class=\"syntax--punct